sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as text-generation-router<br/>8033/TCP gRPC | 3000/TCP HTTP
    participant Batcher as Batching Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant Shard0 as text-generation-server<br/>Shard 0 (UDS)
    participant ShardN as text-generation-server<br/>Shard N (UDS)
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: Text Generation Request (Unary)
    Client->>Router: gRPC Generate(BatchedGenerationRequest)<br/>8033/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate (temp, top_k, top_p,<br/>sequence lengths, stop sequences)
    Router->>Batcher: Enqueue validated request
    Batcher->>Shard0: gRPC Prefill(Batch)<br/>UDS /tmp/text-generation-server-0
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass<br/>(flash/paged attention)
    GPU-->>Shard0: Logits + KV cache
    Shard0-->>Batcher: PrefillResponse
    loop Until EOS or max_new_tokens
        Batcher->>Shard0: gRPC NextToken(batches, cached_batch)
        Shard0->>GPU: CUDA decode step
        GPU-->>Shard0: Next token logits
        Shard0-->>Batcher: NextTokenResponse
    end
    Batcher-->>Router: Completed generation
    Router-->>Client: GenerationResponse<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: Multi-GPU Tensor Parallel Inference
    Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL AllReduce<br/>29500/TCP (intra-pod, plaintext)
    ShardN->>GPU: CUDA forward pass (partial)
    GPU-->>ShardN: Partial results
    ShardN-->>Shard0: NCCL AllReduce result

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Streaming Generation
    Client->>Router: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>8033/TCP server-streaming
    Router->>Batcher: Enqueue streaming request
    loop Token-by-token
        Batcher->>Shard0: gRPC NextToken<br/>UDS
        Shard0->>GPU: CUDA decode
        GPU-->>Shard0: Token
        Shard0-->>Batcher: NextTokenResponse
        Batcher-->>Router: Token generated
        Router-->>Client: GenerationResponse (streamed)<br/>gRPC server-stream
    end

    Note over Client,HFHub: Model Loading (startup)
    Shard0->>HFHub: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Optional auth token
    HFHub-->>Shard0: Model artifacts (safetensors)
    Shard0->>GPU: Load weights to GPU memory
